-- Mellanox Rises to Record, Closing Gap With U.S. Shares
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-02-16T15:14:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-16/mellanox-rises-to-record-in-tel-aviv-closing-gap-to-u-s-shares.html
Mellanox Technologies Ltd. (MLNX)  advanced
to the highest level since the shares started trading, closing
the gap with the U.S. stocks of the Israeli adapter maker.  The  shares  advanced 2.1 percent to 143.80 shekels, or the
equivalent of $38.14, at the 4:30 p.m. close in  Tel Aviv , the
highest level since July 2007. The U.S.-traded shares closed at
$38.11 yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
